6:
Okay, I'm all ready to go! Are people
starting to come in?
9:
That they are. The crowd's so big we
got roped into helping again.
13:
Oh, come on. You make it sound like
you're not having fun doing this,
Nimbus!
17:
Having fun? Ooh, did Nimbus
become a fan of mine as well?
19:
I guess I'll have to give him an
autograph next! "To Nimby, with
love!"
23:
All right, all right. Enough foolin'
around. Let's go.
27:
Sorry for the wait, everyone. The
photo shoot event will be starting
now!
30:
H-hello. It's nice to meet you. Um, I,
uh, don't know what to do...
33:
Oh wow! You're the first person
today! Thank you so much for
coming out. Let's take a picture!
36:
Let's make a heart with our hands!
Come on!
41:
Yep, that's perfect! We'll have
ourselves a magical picture—say
cheese!
44:
Wow... Thank you so much! I'll
treasure it forever!
46:
Hi, Number 6! I'd like to get five
photos with you today!
49:
Gosh, you bought that many? You
must be a huge fan. I'm so happy!
51:
But make sure you don't overspend,
okay? I don't want you to put
yourself in a bad spot because of
my events!
54:
Of course! Don't worry—I only spent
one third of my paycheck!
57:
Man. Lily's got some... intense,
dedicated fans, huh?
61:
I mean, she's a fan-pleaser. It makes
sense that people love her!
74: Oh! You came again! Thank you!
77:
Yeah. I even bought a ticket this
time.
78:
I feel bad... Having someone like me
for a fan is probably nothing but
trouble...
80:
No, no. It's no trouble at all. I'm really
happy that you came out to support
me!
85:
Being all friendly with someone like
him... This idol girl is a weirdo too!
91:
Don't you dare say anything bad
about Number 6! She's a wonderful
and kind idol!
92:
And besides, you guys probably only
came back because you secretly
like her too!
95:
You're... you're just an idiot! Keep
your mouth shut, weirdo!
97: I'm sorry for making a scene...
99:
Don't worry about it, you did great
there! And you seem more full of
energy than before!
102:
It's because I met you, Number 6. I...
I'm going to continue being your fan!
105:
Ooh, thank you! Haha. Okay, let's
take our picture. Cheese!
110:
Good work today, Lily. Let's get
started with the clean up!
115:
I'm going to step away for a
moment!
125:
Hey, everyone! Thank you so much
for coming out today. I know this is
quite sudden, but I'd like to perform
one more song!
128: No way! This must be our lucky day!
131:
This will be a precious memory—for
me and for you!
139:
Well, this certainly wasn't planned...
Is it okay for her to do this?
143:
I mean, they all seem super into it,
so... why not. She announced it,
there's no going back now.
147:
What are we doing standing
around? We've got to turn on the
equipment! Let's help out!
151:
Everyone! I hope you'll become even
bigger fans of both me and
Franchouchou!
157:
What are you doing skulking off on
your own? It's not like you.
160:
You can't run from me, pipsqueak.
I'm good at finding people.
163: I'm not a pipsqueak! I'm Lily!
164:
I was just... thinking about how I
might have to say goodbye to
everyone in this world.
171:
Well... I was looking at everyone
today, smiling and having a good
time. I think if I left they would all be
really sad.
173:
I know what it's like to say goodbye
to someone you love. It's... a lonely
feeling.
177:
All the more reason to do as much
as you can before your time's up,
yeah? Besides, it's either keep going,
or quit, and I doubt you'd do the
latter.
181:
Hehe. Yeah, that's right. You're more
observant than you look, Nimbus!
184:
I've been working for you for a while
now, haven't I? I pick up on things.
187:
You do! All right, I'm going to work
even harder to get more people to
like Franchouchou forever, even if I
end up leaving!
190:
Even if we're in totally different
places, far apart, if they have me in
their hearts... that's enough.
